    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Troglodytes forced to undergo fleshwarping by the drow, ghonhatines harken to what troglodytes might have been in savage prehistory. They stand over 10 feet tall (hunched to about 8 feet) and weigh upward of 5,000 pounds."
        }
    ],
